commit message: Added many icons.
Addes shapes for buttons/lists/backgrounds.

Added background image, updated license texts.

Renamed imageView1 to imageview_logo.
Layout change for fragment_fex_detail.
Implemented adding/editing/removing FSets for the new layout.
Data model is now capable of saving whether a FSet has been done or not.

Data model: implemented clone() for FSet.

Also added a test for that.
Bugfix for FSet.clone() and its tests.
Added Method (+ Test) for FitnessExercise.isTrainingEntryFinished().

Added small versions of all exercise images.

Removed unused icon.
Added icon_square_blue and icon_square_green

Implemented a custom ListAdapter for FExListFragment.

So the current status(finished/not finished) of each exercise can be displayed.
Design change for list_row_fex and list_row_fex_done
FExListAdapter: The listview now shows the number of unfinished/missing FSets.
Fixed some LINT issues.
Added exercise-finished dialog.
Added Workout-finished message.

Fixed layout of fitness exercise list.

Long exercise names wont destroy the layout anymore.
Preparing beta release 0.3.2.
Added some muscle graphics.
Started to implement a dialog for selecting a specific muscle.
Added the missing image files for the SelectMuscleDialog.
SelectMuscleDialog: the selected muscle will now be stored as mMuscle.
Moved SelectMuscleDialog to a different package.
FExDetailFragment: removed unnecessary menu items.
Bugfix TrainingEntryListAdapter: fixed deleting entries.

Added example Workout.

It will be shown when there are no other workouts.
DialogFragmentAddEntry: the textview can now switch between 'add entry' and 'edit entry'
Bugfix DialogFragmentAddEntry. Switching between 'create entry' and 'edit entry' didnt work.
Preparing release v0.4
